org.mapsforge.android.maps.overlay
Class OverlayWay

java.lang.Object
  org.mapsforge.android.maps.overlay.OverlayWay

public class OverlayWay
extends Object

OverlayWay holds all parameters of a single way on a WayOverlay. All rendering parameters like color, stroke width, pattern and transparency can be configured via two Paint objects. Each way is drawn twice - once with each paint object - to allow for different outlines and fillings. The drawing quality can be improved by enabling anti-aliasing.

The way data is represented as a two-dimensional array in order to support multi-polygons. A multi-polygon consists of several polygons and can for example be used to draw a polygon with holes. Each array element on the first level stores on the second level the coordinates of one polygon.
